quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  35,41,Mazima Katonda awanirira eggulu omusanvu n'ensi bibe nga tebivaawo era singa bivaawo teyandibiwaniridde omulala yenna oluvanyuma lwe anti mazima yye wa kisa musonyiyi nnyo
  35,42,"(Abakaafiiri be Makkah) baalayira Katonda mu kukakasa ebirayiro byabwe (ne bagamba nti) singa omutiisa alibajjira bagenda kubeerera ddala abasinga obulungamu okusinga (abantu bonna abaali babaddewo), awo nno omutiisa (Muhammad) bwe yabajjira tekyabongera okugyako okwesamba (omubaka)"
  35,43,"(Nga ekyo kiva) ku kwekuluntaza (kwa bwe) mu nsi, n'okukolala enkwe embi, enkwe embi tezituusa kabi okugyako ku ba nannyini zo olwo abaffe balina kyebalindirira okugyako enkola eyatuuka ku baabakulembera ate nga enkola ya Katonda (mu kubonereza abajeemu) tebaamu kukyusibwa era nga enkola ya Katonda toyinza kugisangamu kujjululwa"
  35,44,"Abaffe tebatambula mu nsi olwo nno nebalaba enkomerero yaabo abaabakulembera nga bwe yali ate nga baali ba maanyi okubasinga, kikafuuwe ekintu kyonna mu ggulu omusanvu ne mu nsi okulemesa Katonda anti mazima yye bulijjo mumanyi nnyo muyinza"
  35,45,Singa Katonda yali avunaana abantu olw'ebyo bye baba bakoze teyaalirese ku ngulu kwayo (ensi) kitambula kyonna naye abalindiriza okutuusa ekiseera ekigere olwo nno entuuko za bwe bwe zituuka (buli muntu nazzibwa eri ekifo ekimusaanira) anti Katonda bulijjo alabira ddala ebikwata ku baddube
  36,1,Yaasin
  36,2,Ndayidde Kur’ani (eno) ejjudde ebigambo eby'amagezi
  36,3,Mazima ggwe (Muhammad) oli wa mu babaka
  36,4,(Nga oli) ku kkubo eggolokofu
  36,5,(Kur’ani eno) yassibwa nantakubwa ku mukono omusaasizi
  36,6,Obe nga otiisa abantu bakadde baabwe abataatiisibwa olwo nno nebaba abeesuulirayo ogwa naggamba (ku bikwata ku Katonda)
  36,7,Mazima kikakase ekigambo (eky'okubonerezebwa) ku basinga obungi mu bo nebaba nga tebagenda kukkiriza
  36,8,"Mazima ffe twassa mu nsingo zaabwe enkoligo nga nazo zituukira ddala ku bulevu, olwo nno nebaba nga balalambadde"
  36,9,"Netussa mu maaso gaabwe ekiziyiza netussa n'ekiziyiza (ekirala) emabega waabwe, olwo nno netubabikka nga bo tebayinza kulaba"
  36,10,Era kyekimu ku bo obatiisizza oba tobatiisizza si baakukkiriza
  36,11,Mazima otiisa oyo agoberera okubuulirira era n'atya (Katonda) omusaasizi ennyo awamu n'okuba nga talabika kale nno musanyuse n'amawulire g’ekisonyiwo n'empeera eyeesiimisa
  36,12,Mazima ffe tuliramusa abafu era tuwandiika ebyo bye baakulembeza ne bye baagoberezaako nga na buli kintu twakikomeka mu kitabo e kikulu e kigenda okulaga buli kimu
  36,13,Bakubire ekifaanayi ky'abantu bo mu kitundu ekimu bwe bajjirwa ababaka
  36,14,"Mu kiseera bwe twatumira gye bali ababaka babiri ne babalimbisa, olwo nno netubongera amaanyi n’owokusatu (bonsatule) nebagamba nti mazima ffe tutumiddwa gye muli"
  36,15,"(Abo mu kitundu ekyo) ne bagamba nti: mmwe temuli okugyako (okuba) bantu bannaffe era Katonda omusaasizi ennyo tassanga kintu kyonna temuli mmwe okugyako okuba nga mulimba (bulimbi)"
  36,16,(Ababaka) nebagamba nti Mukama omulabirizi waffe omanyi nti mazima ddala ffe tutumiddwa gye muli
  36,17,Era tetuvunaanyizibwa okugyako okutuusa obubaka mu bunnyonnyofu
  36,18,"(Abo mu kitundu) nebagamba nti mazima ffe tutya okutuukibwako obuzibu ku lwa mmwe, bwe muteekomeko tujja kubakasukira amayinja era ebibonerezo ebiruma ennyo bijja kubatuukako nga biva gye tuli"
  36,19,(Ababaka) ne bagamba nti okutya kwa mmwe okutuukibwako obuzibu mwe mukyereetedde (bwe mugaanye okuwuliriza obubaka bwe muleeteddwa) wabula mmwe muli bantu abayitirivu mu kwonoona
  36,20,"olwo nno omusajja najja nga ava ku nkomerero y’ekibuga nga ayanguwa naagamba nti: abange bantu bange mugoberere ababaka"
  36,21,Mugoberere abo abatabasaba mpeera ate nga bo balungamu
  36,22,"Nina ki okuba nti sisinza oyo eyantonda, ate nga gyali gye mulizzibwa"
  36,23,"Ndeke Katonda neeteerewo ebisinzibwa ebirala, so nga singa Katonda omusaasizi ennyo anjagaliza akabi okuwolereza kwabyo tekwandingasizza kintu kyonna era tebiyinza kunziruukirira"
  36,24,(Singa nkikola) mazima nze olwo njakuba mu bubuze obweyolefu
  36,25,Mazima nze nzikiriza Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe kale mumpulirize
  36,26,"Naagambibwa (nga amaze okufa) nti yingira e jjana, naagamba nti kale singa abantu bange bamanyi"
  36,27,Ekyo Mukama omulabirizi wange kyansonyiyidde era nanteeka mwabo abagabulwa (olwaleero)